data.description: Must see this 5 bedroom 3 bath 2 story home located on a corner lot in the heart of Hesperia. 1 bedroom 1 bath  downstairs. Open kitchen comes with stainless steel appliances including a refrigerator. Nice walk-in pantry. Family room with fireplace. Separate  living room. Upstairs includes a good size loft and laundry room, washer and dryer to remain. Large master bedroom with his and hers walk-in  closets. Large backyard completely fenced. 2-car attached garage. Close to schools, shopping, and the freeway. Solar panels + Water softener.
